make combination ref matrix to assess intermixing

Source: R/utils.R
make_comb_ref.Rd

make combination ref matrix to assess intermixing

make_comb_ref(ref_mat, if_log = TRUE, sep = "_and_")

Arguments

ref_mat

reference expression matrix
if_log

whether input data is natural
sep

separator for name combinations

Value

expression matrix

Examples

make_comb_ref(
  cbmc_ref,
  sep = "_+_"
)
